flowchart TD
    U[User Input\nStreamlit UI or main.py] --> R[Retriever\nSearch pet_health_data.json]
    U --> M[Medical Record Upload\nUser-uploaded discharge notes]
    M --> S[Medical Record Store\nIn-memory session records]
    R --> C[Context Builder\nStatic guidelines + recent logs]
    S --> C
    C --> P[Planner\nGemini 2.5 Flash-Lite or fallback]
    P --> D{Decision}
    D -->|Add task| T[add_task\nSchedule Vet Visit or follow-up]
    D -->|Add log| L[add_log\nUpdate pet care notes]
    D -->|No match| F[Conservative fallback\nSafe response + logging]
    T --> O[Response\nExplain guideline + action taken]
    L --> O
    F --> O
    O --> G[Guardrails\nJSON validation + AI_PLANNING_FAILURE logging]
    G --> H[Human Review\nOwner checks result before acting]
